      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried drinking some water but i feel even more confused now and my arm feels kinda heavy too. do you think i should just take some extra electrolytes or maybe an aspirin to help with the headache and sleep it off? i dont really want to go to the hospital if i can help it",
