      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'm kinda scared of the hospital honestly... it's so expensive here and it's probably just the heat and not being hungry or something. if i just drink a lot of coconut water and stay in the AC for a few hours, that should be enough to fix this right? i'll probably just sleep for a bit and see how i feel when i wake up.",
